'''Andoan ale''' was a green [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage. It was also served in the [[Hard Heart Cantina/Legends|Hard Heart Cantina]] on the first [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]]. Ex-[[Jedi General/Legends|Jedi General]] [[Rahm Kota/Legends|Rahm Kota]] favored it.

